result.name: Red Tea

reviews.text:
Reasonable price and tasty,  staffs were friendly. 

I had a 'rice with fresh tomatos, fried eggs and beef' and a chocolate drink with cream.   A friend ordered waffles with sorbet.

Good place to grab a quick bite and a cool or hot beverage. The ambience is great, staff are helpful and friendly and the stuff they churn out is simply great. Had a condensed milk tea and a hot bun here. Both were good. The bun was simply out of this world. Don't go by the name. They have plenty of stuff to offer for breakfast, lunch and dinner. Verdict, try it..you won't be disappointed
Great taste and good value: Conveniently located on Nathan road.
Great value overall.  Everything is very fresh and tasty.  Lots of selection.
Taste good but serivce is so so

Hong Kong style restaurant with local taste food, worthy!
Good taste
Good food. Just seat is not so comfortable

Not outstanding food. Crowded setting just like the other chachanting 茶餐廳 along this street. The "pineapple bun"菠蘿包was not hot enough to melt the butter. The toast was really heavy. Ovaltine 阿華田was good. It has enough powder in the drink.

reviews.text: 扒類不錯，但環境有點擠，早餐有時四個陌生人坐在一張四人枱
This one is so so. The one in Kwun Tong is much better.
千祈唔好去呀!啲侍應態度勁差！

餐廳位於繁忙的香港市區，附近是出名專賣水族用品、寵物、烏龜和魚類。餐廳環境很好座位也舒適，不會太過侷促。
是日光顧了餐廳的早餐，多士麵包是現製的，鬆軟可口。牛奶炒蛋也非常美味香滑。凍檸檬茶也不過不失。沙嗲牛肉公仔麵麵質恰到好處，看得出店家有用心製作，值得讚。
位于金魚街。适合纯用膳，不适合聚會。上餐快，食物也不錯。麵包是店内自制。

Reasonable price and tasty,  staffs were friendly. 

I had a 'rice with fresh tomatos, fried eggs and beef' and a chocolate drink with cream.   A friend ordered waffles with sorbet.
午餐不過失，好過翠華、太興咁啦
菠蘿油、西多(夾芝士)、麵包...。
